ay. We execute on our vision and mission through three strategic priorities.\nOUR CUSTOMERS OUR PEOPLE OUR PERFORMANCE Enhance their experience with Xcel Energy \nand keep their bills as low as possible Provide a rewarding employee experience, \nwith development, engagement and growth  ...    Our values, culture and Code of Conduct serve as the foundation upon which X"
