ory decisions. Q3: What retrofits provide the highest ROI?A3: LED lighting, HVAC optimization, insulation, controls, and dock system upgrades. Q4: How can tenants protect themselves?A4: Negotiate CAM caps, co-funded upgrades, and audit rights. Q5: Where do I start?A5: Begin with a comprehensive energy audit to benchmark current usage and plan improvements.  ...    - Facebook: Aviva Sonenreich’s Denver Commercial Real Estate| Warehouse Hotline - X (Twitter): Aviva – Denver – Warehouse\n- TikTok: @avivarealestate  ...    Let’s Talk!\n\n#### Sources: - U.S. Department of Energy – Prologis Case Study\n- U.S. Engineering Energy Services - Colorado Public Utilities Commission – Xcel Energy Rate Case Filing ##### Warehouse Hotline The Warehouse Hotline is Denver’s leading industrial brokerage, focused exclusively on warehouses and industrial land. We know the submarkets, the tenants, the pricing, and the deals because industrial is all we do. [The Office Crisis & Why Work Feels Broken With Cali Williams Yost – RFP"
